%setADSMeta(
    members  = adsmeta.adae
  , vars     = ASTDT
  , deri_txt = "Derived from AE.AESTDTC. Incomplete dates will be imputed using the following rules: If the active treatment start date falls within imputation range, incomplete AE start date will be imputed as the active treatment start date. If the active treatment start date does not fall within the imputation range, and the placebo treatment start date falls within the imputation range, an incomplete AE start date is imputed as the placebo treatment start date. Otherwise, the partially missing AE start date will be imputed to the earliest date of the imputation range. Completely missing start date will not be imputed."
);

