/*
 * Purpose          : Change from baseline in mean daily frequency of moderate to severe hot flashes - MMRM analysis - by treatment group (FAS)
 * Programming Spec :
 * Validation Level : 2 - Double programming  ,
 * SAS Version      : Linux 9.4
 *******************************************************************************
